item.title: CES2019 Phone Survey Falsely Predicts The Conservative Party Can Win the Election
item.description: Authorship Henry Cheng Abstract The Liberal Party won the 2019 federal election. In the study, we explore the ces2019 phone survey data set. We found out that the survey result actually favor on the Conservative Party Introduction We use Wickham et al. (2019), R Core Team (2020), Allaire et al. (2020), Wickham, Hester, and Chang (2020), Hodgetts and Alexander (2020), Xie (2020) The Canadian Liberal Party won the 2019 Federal Election by getting 46.
